; Coverage test for report.cc
; When --output is set, color and pager are disabled even if explicitly set.
; HANDLER(color).off when --output is used
; HANDLER(pager_).off when --output is used
; Using --output=/dev/stdout so output still goes to stdout for capture.

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg --color --pager=cat --output=/dev/stdout
24-Jan-01 Test                  Expenses:Food                $10.00       $10.00
                                Assets:Cash                 $-10.00            0
end test
